    dc:description "Figure 11. A leaf blade Magnolia amazonica B trichomes from the petiole of M. amazonica C Magnolia brasiliensis D fruit with trichomes in M. brasiliensis E leaf blade M. brasiliensis F Magnolia ovata showing perule G floral bud of M. ovata H leaf blade of M. ovata I M. ovata mature fruit. (A-B: A. M Barreto 30; C-E: A. A. Grillo & M. Sztutman> s. n.; F-G: E. P. Heringer, 8726; H: R. R. Rodrigues et al. 161; I: based on photographs of J. C. J Barbosa.) Drawing prepared by Klei Souza." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/977400" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.238.113277.figure12>
    dc:description "Figure 12. A Magnolia irwiniana B presence of flower bud in M. irwiniana C leaf blade of M. irwiniana D detail of branch and stipule with trichomes in M. irwiniana E detail of the trichomes on the petiolar scars F immature fruit of M. irwiniana G detail of the puberulent trichomes on the fruit H Magnolia sellowiana I leaf blade M. sellowiana. (A: based on photographs of D. A. Zavatin; B: based on photographs of J. C. J. Barbosa C-G: H. F Leitao Filho et al. 34821; H: based on photographs of D. A. Zavatin; I: M. Kuhlmann 1809) Drawing prepared by Klei Souza." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/977401" ;
